Author: blimpopotamus
Text: the literal meaning of *anorexia* is “without hunger,” which sounds like what you’re describing. based on the symptoms you described, it doesn’t sound like you have the typical version of anorexia seen on this sub, but you’re not well, either. please talk to a doctor.

Author: BabyBaphomet_
Text: I would call that an eating disorder. Lots of people have "weird" EDs, it's called EDNOS. I think thats where you are on the spectrum.          Definitely recommend seeing a doctor. It is unhealthy to be underweight, even if it's not bc of anorexia.
